        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Bangkok/scene_zika.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository df152624-1678-4688-ae63-4ddbfe21823d).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening 47, your target is Tarrin, also known as &quot;The Pest&quot;. Under the guise of a fumigation employee Tarrin has managed to snatch and auction off thousands of dollars in stolen goods from those oblivious to his practices. With the help of a couple of paid off employees, Tarrin has began his next big hit in the form of the Himmapan Hotel. \r\rYour secondary target is Wichian Liang, a milita member hired  by both SIster Yulduz &amp; Tarrin for protection.\r\rGood luck 47, I&apos;ll leave you to prepare.",
